{
  "stem": "9168.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I especially had this-- this specialty in medical terminology that I had in court reporting.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I-- I got a response from the War Department that I was well qualified in all areas except I was too young.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was only 20, and I had to be 21.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I knew I just had to wait until I was 21.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the meantime, they had gotten-- they had recruited their reporters to get over there and start Goering's trial.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Some of them were from the military, court reporters who were already in Europe.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- but they recruited most of them as civilians who were old enough.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Soon as I was 21, they told me I could go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I was 21, of course, by that time the reporters were already there for Goering's trial.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And at the processing and my getting cholera and tetanus shots and passing the US Civil Service Examination at 200 words per minute, that was the high, you know, the required speed, I-- I was accepted.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Signed a contract for one year-- until my memory came to recently, I felt that it was a two-year contract, but it was a one year.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember saying-- thinking if I signed up for a one year, I could always extend it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And did.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not at all, other then we had begun-- begun to see on Movietone newsreels the pictures of devastated German cities, Nuremberg included.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I knew I was going to be going to a bombed out city.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's all.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But in my office in Detroit, there were two other court reporters who, and when I was 20 years old, they were-- one was 30 and one was 40, and who were accepted-- applied and were accepted, too, who actually preceded me.",
      "word_count": 42
    }
  ],
